    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <i>Fred Johnson's: Mech Simulator</i>, you pilot a powerful mech on the world of Blue Mirage IV. After your freighter is shot down while responding to a distress beacon, you and your mercenary crew must scavenge supplies, fortify a beachside camp, and explore a mysterious island filled with ancient defenses, hostile forces, and the remnants of a lost human settlement. Engage in  battles, solve environmental puzzles, and uncover the secrets of this alien world as you fight to repair your ship and escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch out for enemy pirates and looters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278130/extras/a938a31d859f0f8b3739ea3dd1ba9860.poster.avif?t=1746625622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278130/extras/a938a31d859f0f8b3739ea3dd1ba9860.webm?t=1746625622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278130/extras/a938a31d859f0f8b3739ea3dd1ba9860.mp4?t=1746625622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Important buildings can be destroyed with targeted firepower!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278130/extras/e3181e40a12eb85f5279e1dc3e017109.poster.avif?t=1746625622\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3278130/extras/e3181e40a12eb85f5279e1dc3e017109.webm?t=1746625622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.s